OL,3,CHealth Secretary 'shocked' police boss
OL,4,Cstill in post after Maccabi ban errors
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting added
OL,7,Fhis voice, saying he was "absolutely
OL,8,Fshocked" that the chief constable
OL,9,Fremained in post - after a highly
OL,10,Fcritical review into how his force
OL,11,Fhandled the decision to ban Maccabi
OL,12,FTel Aviv fans from a match in
OL,13,FBirmingham on 6 November.
OL,15,FHe also said he would be "horrified"
OL,16,Fif Guildford is still in post by the
OL,17,Fend of the day, adding his failure to
OL,18,Fresign was "a stain on his character".
OL,20,FLikewise, Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy
OL,21,Fsaid she was "astonished".
