OL,6,FSpeaking in the House of Commons,
OL,7,FNandy said: "Having watched West
OL,8,FMidlands Police contradict me,
OL,9,Fcontradict this Government and
OL,10,Fcontradict their own evidence in
OL,11,Fpublic over recent months, and seeing
OL,12,Fall of that laid bare in a report that
OL,13,Fthe Home Secretary brought to this
OL,14,FHouse yesterday, I do want to say to
OL,15,Fhim that I believe it is astonishing
OL,16,Fthat the chief constable remains in
OL,17,Fpost and I hope he will seriously
OL,18,Freflect."
