OL,3,CHealth Secretary 'shocked' police boss
OL,4,Cstill in post after Maccabi ban errors
OL,6,FCurrently, it is only police and crime
OL,7,Fcommissioners (PCCS) who hold the
OL,8,Fpower to dismiss a chief constable.
OL,10,FLabour PCC Simon Foster did not sack
OL,11,Fthe chief constable on Wednesday,
OL,12,Fsaying he wanted to give "all these
OL,13,Fissues full and proper consideration"
OL,14,Fand was waiting for a report by the
OL,15,FHome Affairs Select Committee.
OL,17,FFoster said he wants to question
OL,18,FGuildford at a meeting of his
OL,19,Faccountability and governance board
OL,20,Fheld in public on 27 January.
