OL,6,FHe acknowledged the "significant
OL,7,Fstrength of feeling" about the issue,
OL,8,Fadding: "In consideration of these
OL,9,Fmatters, it is vital that all involved
OL,10,Fact in accordance with due process and
OL,11,Fthe law at all times."
OL,13,FIn a statement on Thursday, Home
OL,14,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood said: "When
OL,15,Fa chief constable is responsible for a
OL,16,Fdamaging failure of leadership, the
OL,17,Fpublic rightly expect the Home
OL,18,FSecretary to act. And I intend to
OL,19,Frestore their ability to do so.
