OL,6,F"This government will soon reintroduce
OL,7,Fthe Home Secretary's power to dismiss
OL,8,Fchief constables."
OL,10,FMahmood promised to make police
OL,11,Fleaders accountable to Parliament and
OL,12,Fthe public ahead of sweeping police
OL,13,Freforms to be announced later this
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FA spokesman for Number 10 said it no
OL,17,Flonger had confidence in Guildford's
OL,18,Fposition as chief constable, but it
OL,19,Fwas "ultimately a decision" for the
OL,20,FPCC but that "this decision should be
OL,21,Ffor the Home Secretary."
