OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Chief Inspector of
OL,7,FConstabulary Sir Andy Cooke found
OL,8,Fsignificant leadership failings after
OL,9,Fthe force recommended banning Maccabi
OL,10,FTel Aviv fans from attending a Europa
OL,11,FLeague match at Aston Villa.
OL,13,FHe said several "inaccuracies" had
OL,14,Fbeen included in a report to
OL,15,FBirmingham's safety advisory group,
OL,16,Fincluding reference to a non-existent
OL,17,Ffixture between between Maccabi Tel
OL,18,FAviv and West Ham.
